{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"1aca887a93","title":"“五一”节和张×的谈话","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"cb685ec319","index":0,"year":1967,"month":5,"day":1,"articleId":"1aca887a93"}],"tags":[{"id":"314ad57c4d","name":"对话","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"c20d333791","name":"关键人物文稿","type":"文稿大类"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"wansui5","name":"毛泽东思想万岁(1961-1968卷)","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"未知","files":"/books/wansui5a.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"wansui5":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"e581098855","type":"title","text":"“五一”节和张×的谈话","index":0,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"1aca887a93"},{"id":"1de84e982a","type":"paragraph","text":"五月一日晚上十点三十五分在天安门城楼上，江青同志向毛主席、林副主席单独引见了张×，接见时周总理也在座。","index":1,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"1aca887a93"},{"id":"effd1c4154","type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席、林副主席和张×亲切握手。毛主席红光满面，神采奕奕，身体非常健康。这是中国人民和世界人民的最大幸福。","index":2,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"1aca887a93"},{"id":"f6b1155b88","type":"paragraph","text":"江青同志向毛主席．林付主席介绍说：这是国家科委张×，她们把韩光一伙打倒了，她们那里运动搞得不错。","index":3,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"1aca887a93"},{"id":"2089841027","type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席说：应该祝科委同志们万寿无疆，应该祝人民万寿无疆！","index":4,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"1aca887a93"},{"id":"5d6663f705","type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席又说：女同志也一样造反嘛！你们把反革命韩光打倒了，你们夺权夺得好！","index":5,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"1aca887a93"},{"id":"ce14ead96d","type":"paragraph","text":"接着主席又亲切地问：你现在担任什么工作？","index":6,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"1aca887a93"},{"id":"f2890b3bdc","type":"paragraph","text":"张×同答说：在国家科委革命委员会工作。","index":7,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"1aca887a93"},{"id":"d0f4accc56","type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席问：是革命委员会主任吧？","index":8,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"1aca887a93"},{"id":"b010dcc131","type":"paragraph","text":"周总理说：也就是了吧！","index":9,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"1aca887a93"},{"id":"ee768b9ecf","type":"paragraph","text":"这时，毛主席向林副主席说：她原来是个局长，和群众一起造反。","index":10,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"1aca887a93"}],"page":{"id":"a8cee8ba6e","publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"1aca887a93","start":588,"end":588}}}},"__N_SSG":true}